title: Ten Must Have Essential Bluegrass Albums [-emidius-]
description:
The included are considered by many to be some of the top essential Bluegrass albums of all time. Bluegrass was not an easy genre to tacle, so I have tried to make sure I included a cross section of the best Bluegrass. Regardless of any album rankings...these are truly MUST OWN albums for anyone interested in Bluegrass. I hope you enjoy this collection and I will be releasing further collections in the near future.

1. Alison Krauss & Union Station - New Favorite


2. Bela Fleck - Drive


3. Bill Monroe - The Essential Bill Monroe & His Blue Grass Boys


4. Blue Highway - Through The Window Of a Train


5. Jerry Garcia, David Grisman - Old And In The Way


6. John Hartford - Aereo-plain


7. Seldom Scene - Act 1


8. Tony Rice - Manzanita


9. Bluegrass Mandolin Extravaganza


10. Shabba Ranks - As Raw As Ever
